    "title": "Opening for Production Engineer at Emami Digital Technologies",
    "description": "We at Emami Digital Technologies are looking for an experienced Production Engineer based out of Delhi. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Emami Digital Technologies:\nEmami Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Manage supplier quality audits and vendor development\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in SAP MM/PP\n• Proficiency in GD&T\n• Proficiency in 5S\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Kaizen\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Delhi, Delhi, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Emami Digital Technologies!",
